3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%C3%A1n/T%E1%BB%91ng-t%C4%83ng-quy-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-B%E1%BA%A3n/poem-ORMH2kwjRixsi8KCuvyI4A">Tống tăng quy Nhật Bản - 送僧歸日本</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%C3%A1n/author-GPZDeWO7_HplSvFSozfFjg">Phương Cán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%AD-Hoan-lai-kinh-h%E1%BB%99i-th%C3%AD-ph%C3%BA-thi-ho%E1%BA%A1-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn-d%C4%A9-t%E1%BA%B7ng/poem-hTZxrGZ3c2FIhNwRV0p5fw">Tử Hoan lai kinh hội thí phú thi hoạ nguyên vận dĩ tặng - 子懽來京會試賦詩和元韻以贈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BA%A1c-mi%E1%BA%BFu-to%E1%BA%A1i-t%C3%BAc-nh%E1%BA%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-m%C3%B4n-l%C3%A2u/poem-Fi0Gv61h-zHA0H8Q_95dwg">Yết Hành nhạc miếu toại túc nhạc tự đề môn lâu - 謁衡岳廟遂宿嶽寺題門樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
